-- Hong Kong Imposes New Duty on Property Resold Within Two Years of Purchase
-- B y   S o p h i e   L e u n g
-- 2010-11-19T08:51:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-19/hong-kong-imposes-new-duty-on-property-resold-within-two-years-of-purchase.html
Hong Kong will impose a new stamp
duty on the resale of property within two years of its initial
purchase, Financial Secretary John Tsang said today.  To contact the reporter on this story:
